your opinion?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="39841" author="behlendorf" created="Fri, 1 Jun 2012 15:13:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue prompted me to simply manual remove the logs and hit ORI-690&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
